{"tid":1800473,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林志偉：「『和理非』滅絕人性，冷血程度不下於施暴狂徒！！」","createTime":"2019-12-27T23:11:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-28T08:38:22.000Z","uid":202464,"like":3,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"ff696bc53763db2d72414950b24763f793dcfa4b","tid":1800473,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T23:11:26.000Z","msg":"警察隊員佐級協會主席林志偉向會員發信：<br />\n<br />\n1. 不但參與暴行的示威者要為其嚴重罪行負上責任，自稱和平、理性、非暴力的追隨者亦難辭其咎，<br />\n<br />\n2. 所謂「和理非」與暴徒形影不離，無處不在，<br />\n<br />\n3. 呼籲傳媒及市民停止以「和理非」稱呼他們，<br />\n<br />\n4. 他們行逕「滅絕人性，冷血程度不下於施暴狂徒」，是赤裸裸的幫凶。"},{"pid":"d9b04412c37397f9f41c90ac46c0faa223ddeec2","tid":1800473,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T23:12:20.000Z","msg":"滅絕人性！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0866f001d460cc9d7d0e718214bdedc08db23639","tid":1800473,"uid":146520,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T23:15:37.000Z","msg":"冇邏輯可言<br />\n根本非勇武市民就係和理非<br />\n淨返果啲不正常撐警廢老就同黑警就唔係人，係曱甴屎"},{"pid":"53c96a9ee95a6cac11cc3a25c9088ea6e52fad73","tid":1800473,"uid":183758,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T23:17:08.000Z","msg":"又想吹風當新疆咁做"},{"pid":"e080879a291239a8f49eb6eb11371bec98132889","tid":1800473,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"53c96a9ee95a6cac11cc3a25c9088ea6e52fad73","tid":1800473,"uid":183758,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T23:17:08.000Z","msg":"又想吹風當新疆咁做"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T23:19:12.000Z","msg":"不嬲都想。"},{"pid":"5b2f1d337b108ac2f652acf008fe4dd2ffb7cda8","tid":1800473,"uid":326897,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T23:20:30.000Z","msg":"助紂為虐嘅黑狗，濫捕濫權冇皇管，<br />\n半年到依家一個黑狗都冇上庭，<br />\n開完槍，車完人，重要話電光火石，<br />\n屌你老母，唔好話返大灣區，<br />\n直頭直接落地獄"},{"pid":"26f651e292e01f46fa52b545071acaa34abcd2f9","tid":1800473,"uid":14494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T23:20:51.000Z","msg":"林大總統又出番黎9 up"},{"pid":"bdde922a55125ebc785551a45e6066a94c617d97","tid":1800473,"uid":16841,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T23:25:33.000Z","msg":"因為和理非死都唔割咪向佢地開刀囉 <br />\n都唔知求左和理非同勇武割蓆幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但連和理非都唔做怨氣只會愈黎愈大 咪試下R爛塊臉屌哂大多數人囉"},{"pid":"7c97d9ab86213857d24eb1d11ebfaaa6b2129c58","tid":1800473,"uid":47492,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0866f001d460cc9d7d0e718214bdedc08db23639","tid":1800473,"uid":146520,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T23:15:37.000Z","msg":"冇邏輯可言<br />\n根本非勇武市民就係和理非<br />\n淨返果啲不正常撐警廢老就同黑警就唔係人，係曱甴屎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T23:25:48.000Z","msg":"佢地想分化"},{"pid":"b41f2c9dc85a553c0c66e0da56fae26c70db0b69","tid":1800473,"uid":202464,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"bdde922a55125ebc785551a45e6066a94c617d97","tid":1800473,"uid":16841,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T23:25:33.000Z","msg":"因為和理非死都唔割咪向佢地開刀囉 <br />\n都唔知求左和理非同勇武割蓆幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但連和理非都唔做怨氣只會愈黎愈大 咪試下R爛塊臉屌哂大多數人囉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T23:36:39.000Z","msg":"有牌黑社會邏輯：<br />\n<br />\n不跪下做奴才的全都定義為暴徒。<br />\n<br />\n等你們全都跪下了，將跪的姿勢不正確的定義為暴徒。<br />\n<br />\n等你們跪下的姿勢都符合要求了，將跪著臉上沒有笑容的定義為暴徒。<br />\n<br />\n等你們跪著笑著對時候，將心裡沒有全然服從的定義為暴徒。"},{"pid":"1d0988afcf600c12e1232194950d950918429e07","tid":1800473,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T23:44:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efba12f14c4ae9f3a5e3eae36ebb4ee09bd0f75d","tid":1800473,"uid":65790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T23:47:26.000Z","msg":"痴線，連和平示威都打壓<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eabb157dfb6dde3ee0c7182f2b46168b3f4f0968","tid":1800473,"uid":72457,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T23:48:06.000Z","msg":"「我認為，對我們來說，一個人，一個黨，一個軍隊，或者一個學校，如若不被敵人反對，那就不好了，那一定是同敵人同流合污了。如若被敵人反對，那就好了，那就證明我們同敵人劃清界線了。如若敵人起勁地反對我們，把我們說得一塌糊塗，一無是處，那就更好了，那就證明我們不但同敵人劃清了界線，而且證明我們的工作是很有成績的了。」[26]<br />\n〈被敵人反對是好事而不是壞事〉，1939年5月26日"},{"pid":"beeb5f34325b2f509a265ff2638a38abc545ed70","tid":1800473,"uid":343821,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T23:53:00.000Z","msg":"呢隻帶眼鏡既肥曱甴能未死啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e198648bf00bf19c2b25986d503a26a0ebff8fa8","tid":1800473,"uid":212509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"beeb5f34325b2f509a265ff2638a38abc545ed70","tid":1800473,"uid":343821,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T23:53:00.000Z","msg":"呢隻帶眼鏡既肥曱甴能未死啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T23:55:05.000Z","msg":"點解半年黎都好似冇見過呢隻曱甴落場<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其實佢係做咩position<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfdef856b77021b8a90d1c5b69f93d8384d37963","tid":1800473,"uid":11809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T23:55:21.000Z","msg":"等俾人制裁啦仆街！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"385b1f67a548936af599595704b4e906bfb6d1da","tid":1800473,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e198648bf00bf19c2b25986d503a26a0ebff8fa8","tid":1800473,"uid":212509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"beeb5f34325b2f509a